==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dumpage
<hw>Dump"age</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act
of dumping loads from carts, especially loads of refuse matter; also, a
heap of dumped matter.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A fee paid for the privilege of dumping loads;
called in some cases <altname>tipping fee</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>dumpcart</ent>⟦br⟧
